data.description: You won't want to miss this adorable ranch style home in Belmont.  It's on a lovely street that is minutes away from the university, shopping and interstate.  Hardwood floors through out the main living area into the bedrooms, tile floors in the kitchen and bathroom.  Kitchen has been updated with updated appliances and a nice eat in dining area.  The backyard is made for entertaining with a covered patio and plenty of grass to play.  It has a shed for storage and a dog pen.  Completely fenced in.  RV parking in the front area and beautiful mature trees to shade your new home.  Please schedule your showing today!
